{"type":"message","id":"15d90f8b","parentId":"5a311dcb","timestamp":"2026-04-01T18:40:05.863Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The learning notes have been saved. Let me also check if there's a need to update the memory index.","thinkingSignature":"639663a7bebdcd4279ea5ea089db68f6b013ee49575615afcfacb9f62bc9e77d"},{"type":"text","text":"**检测到空闲状态，已完成自主学习。**\n\n**已完成**：搜索了企业数字化转型、智能安防、IT运维服务三个领域的最新动态，整理关键信息并保存到 `memory/学习笔记.md`。\n\n**核心要点**：\n- **政策面**：国家200亿专项支持中小企业数字化转型，北京/广东给出量化目标\n- **市场面**：弱电工程市场8000亿规模，AI安防国产化加速（价格低15-30%）\n- **技术面**：AIOps渗透率65%，NaaS模式兴起，运维从\"成本工具\"升级为\"战略支点\""}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4729,"output":150,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48860,"cost":{"input":0.0014187,"output":0.00017999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029181299999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775068801538}}
